data.description: MOVE IN READY 4 Bedroom in sought after Western Branch!  This well-maintained gem has 1st floor open floor plan, oversized living room, dining room, modern bathrooms and kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Desirable 1st floor bedroom and full bath, ideal for remote work or school. Upstairs bedrooms feature new carpet, paint and generous sized closets.  Relax after a long day in your fully fenced in backyard.  Conveniently located near military bases, shipyards, major hospitals, naval hospitals, popular landmarks, entertainment and shopping.  Easy access to freeways, bridges and tunnels.  Contact Agent today to Schedule your Private Showing!
